cql:
library Test136 version '0.0.006'

using QDM version '5.0.2'

valueset "ONC Administrative Sex": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1' 

valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836' 

valueset "Ethnicity": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.837' 

valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591' 

valueset "Narcolepsy": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.114.12.1011' 

valueset "Behavioral Health Follow-up Visit": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1054' 

valueset "Discharge Services- Observation Care": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1039' 

valueset "Encounter Inpatient": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.666.5.307' 

valueset "Face-to-Face Interaction": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1048' 

valueset "Home Healthcare Services": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1016' 

valueset "Hospital Observation Care - Initial": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1002' 

valueset "Inpatient Encounter": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1060' 

valueset "Office Visit": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1001' 

valueset "Outpatient Consultation": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1008' 

valueset "Preventive Care, Established Office Visit, 0 to 17": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1024' 

valueset "Preventive Care Services - Group Counseling": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1027' 

valueset "Preventive Care Services-Individual Counseling": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1026' 

valueset "Preventive Care Services, Initial Office Visit, 0 to 17": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1022' 

valueset "Psych Visit - Diagnostic Evaluation": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1492' 

valueset "Psych Visit - Psychotherapy": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1496' 

valueset "Psychotherapy and Pharmacologic Management": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1055' 

valueset "Telehealth Services": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1031' 

valueset "Telephone Management": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1053' 

valueset "Hospice care ambulatory": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1108.15' 

valueset "ADHD Medications": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.196.12.1171' 

valueset "Substance Abuse": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.106.12.1004' 

valueset "Mental Health Diagnoses": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.105.12.1004' 

valueset "Discharged to Health Care Facility for Hospice Care": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.117.1.7.1.207' 

valueset "Discharged to Home for Hospice Care": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.117.1.7.1.209' 

valueset "Ambulatory": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.122.12.1003' 

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "SDE Ethnicity": ["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer": ["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race": ["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex": ["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Denominator 1": "Initial Population 1"

define "Denominator 2": "Initial Population 2"

define "ADHD Cumulative Medication Duration Greater Than or Equal to 210 Days": "CumulativeMedicationDuration"("ADHD Meds Taken Within 300 Days After First Medication Dispensed") >= 210

define "ADHD Meds Taken Within 300 Days After First Medication Dispensed": ["Medication, Active": "ADHD Medications"] ActiveADHDMedications 
        with "First Medication Dispensed" InitialADHDMedication
            such that ActiveADHDMedications.relevantPeriod starts 300 days or less after InitialADHDMedication.authorDatetime
                or ActiveADHDMedications.relevantPeriod starts same as InitialADHDMedication.authorDatetime

define "ADHD Medication Exclusion": ["Medication, Active": "ADHD Medications"] ActiveADHDMedication
    with "First Medication Dispensed" InitialADHDMedication
        such that ActiveADHDMedication.relevantPeriod starts 120 days or less before InitialADHDMedication.authorDatetime

define "Two or More Followup Encounters": Count("Encounters After Initial ADHD Med") >= 2

define "First Encounter": (["Encounter, Performed": "Office Visit"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Face-to-Face Interaction"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Home Healthcare Services"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Preventive Care, Established Office Visit, 0 to 17"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Preventive Care Services, Initial Office Visit, 0 to 17"]) Encounter 
    where Encounter.relevantPeriod during "Measurement Period"

define "Denominator Exclusions 1": "Hospice Exclusion"
    or exists("Narcolepsy Exclusion")
    or exists("Mental Health Dx Substance Abuse Exclusion 1")
    or exists("ADHD Medication Exclusion")

define "Denominator Exclusions 2": "Hospice Exclusion"
    or exists("Narcolepsy Exclusion")
    or exists("Mental Health Dx Substance Abuse Exclusion 2")
    or exists("ADHD Medication Exclusion")

define "First Medication Dispensed": First(["Medication, Dispensed": "ADHD Medications"] Dispensed
    where Dispensed.authorDatetime 60 days or less after start "Measurement Period"
        or Dispensed.authorDatetime 90 days or less before start "Measurement Period"
        or Dispensed.authorDatetime same as start "Measurement Period" 
    sort by authorDatetime)

define "Hospice Exclusion": exists(["Encounter, Performed": "Encounter Inpatient"] DischargeHospice
    where (DischargeHospice.dischargeDisposition in "Discharged to Home for Hospice Care"
        or DischargeHospice.dischargeDisposition in "Discharged to Health Care Facility for Hospice Care")
    and DischargeHospice.relevantPeriod ends during "Measurement Period")
or exists(["Intervention, Order": "Hospice care ambulatory"] HospiceOrder
    where HospiceOrder.authorDatetime during "Measurement Period")
or exists(["Intervention, Performed": "Hospice care ambulatory"] HospicePerformed
    where HospicePerformed.relevantPeriod overlaps "Measurement Period")

define "Narcolepsy Exclusion": ["Diagnosis": "Narcolepsy"] NarcolepsyDx 
    where NarcolepsyDx.prevalencePeriod starts before end "Measurement Period"

define "Numerator 1": "Encounter 30 days after Initial ADHD Med"

define "Qualifying Encounter": ["Encounter, Performed": "Office Visit"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Hospital Observation Care - Initial"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Preventive Care Services - Group Counseling"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Behavioral Health Follow-up Visit"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Preventive Care Services-Individual Counseling"]
    union (["Encounter, Performed": "Psychotherapy and Pharmacologic Management"] PsychPharmMgmt where PsychPharmMgmt.facilityLocation in "Ambulatory")
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Face-to-Face Interaction"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Discharge Services- Observation Care"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Outpatient Consultation"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Home Healthcare Services"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Preventive Care Services, Initial Office Visit, 0 to 17"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Preventive Care, Established Office Visit, 0 to 17"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Psych Visit - Diagnostic Evaluation"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Psych Visit - Psychotherapy"]

define "Encounters After Initial ADHD Med": "Qualifying Encounter" Encounter 
    with "First Medication Dispensed" InitialADHDMedication 
        such that Encounter.relevantPeriod starts 31 days or more after InitialADHDMedication.authorDatetime 
            and Encounter.relevantPeriod starts 300 days or less after InitialADHDMedication.authorDatetime

define "Mental Health Dx Substance Abuse Exclusion 2": ["Encounter, Performed": "Inpatient Encounter"] Encounter 
    with "First Medication Dispensed" InitalADHDMedication 
        such that Encounter.relevantPeriod starts 300 days or less after InitalADHDMedication.authorDatetime
    where (Encounter.principalDiagnosis in "Mental Health Diagnoses"
        or Encounter.principalDiagnosis in "Substance Abuse")

define "Mental Health Dx Substance Abuse Exclusion 1": ["Encounter, Performed": "Inpatient Encounter"] Encounter 
    with "First Medication Dispensed" InitalADHDMedication 
        such that Encounter.relevantPeriod starts 30 days or less after InitalADHDMedication.authorDatetime
    where (Encounter.principalDiagnosis in "Mental Health Diagnoses"
        or Encounter.principalDiagnosis in "Substance Abuse")

define "Tele Services or Mgmt": (["Encounter, Performed": "Telehealth Services"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Telephone Management"]) TeleEncounter 
    with "First Medication Dispensed" InitialADHDMedication
        such that TeleEncounter.relevantPeriod starts 31 days or more after InitialADHDMedication.authorDatetime
            and TeleEncounter.relevantPeriod starts 300 days or less after InitialADHDMedication.authorDatetime

define "Initial Population 2": "First Medication Dispensed" is not null
    and exists("First Encounter")
    and AgeInYearsAt(start of "Measurement Period") >=6
    and AgeInYearsAt(start of "Measurement Period") <12
    and "ADHD Cumulative Medication Duration Greater Than or Equal to 210 Days"

define "Initial Population 1": "First Medication Dispensed" is not null
    and exists("First Encounter")
    and AgeInYearsAt(start of "Measurement Period") >=6
    and AgeInYearsAt(start of "Measurement Period") <12

define "Encounter 30 days after Initial ADHD Med": exists("Qualifying Encounter" Encounter 
    with "First Medication Dispensed" InitialADHDMedication 
        such that Encounter.relevantPeriod starts 30 days or less after InitialADHDMedication.authorDatetime)

define "Numerator 2": "Encounter 30 days after Initial ADHD Med"
    and (("Two or More Followup Encounters")
        or (exists("Encounters After Initial ADHD Med")
            and exists("Tele Services or Mgmt")))

define function "CumulativeMedicationDuration"(Medication List<"Medication, Active"> ): Sum((collapse(Medication.relevantPeriod)) CMD 
    return duration in days of CMD)
